-- Red Electrica Chairman Seeks Compensation From Bolivia, ABC Says
-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 2012-05-06T12:41:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-06/red-electrica-chairman-seeks-compensation-from-bolivia-abc-says.html
Red Electrica Corp. SA (REE)  Chairman Jose Folgado plans to meet with Bolivia’s energy minister tomorrow to
defend the Spanish company’s interests,  ABC  reported today,
citing an interview with Folgado.  Following the decision by the Andean country to expropriate
Red Electrica’s local unit, Folgado will seek compensation that
includes both the value of the assets and investments made since
2002, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Manuel Baigorri in Madrid at 
 mbaigorri@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  